{"tid":485213,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"Bitcoin 價值","createTime":"2017-11-30T18:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T08:19:54.000Z","uid":13025,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fc9c0de629211ac725c00d20fa699e6e3c3f6d0b","tid":485213,"uid":13025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:26:00.000Z","msg":"今天和同事討論過bitcoin(後略BC)價值問題 同事認為非理性情況下BC價值是無限 而且BC作為deepweb貨幣是有需求 我則認為BC現價是炒作出來 當然我沒證據<br />\n<br />\n我提出的理據是如果BC價值來於deepweb transaction 其價值其實無從估算 deepweb platform理論上不會透明化其平交易 同時不想和其它平台共享交易訊息 在這情況總交易量是無知悉 BC價值不能從其購買力估算出來 反之 每宗BC為交易幣之交易都是參考BC market price作價格估計<br />\n<br />\n但在這情況 為何BC愈升愈有呢 黑市賣性奴10k usd 本來收10個BC而家收1個 賣家係BC實換到USd的情況當然無所謂 但錢莊兌換能力真係咁高？如果BC再升十倍賣家仲夠唔夠膽收BC 我好懷疑<br />\n<br />\n而且 出現左BC 本來deepweb平台的清黑錢角色被取代 佢地接受BC的前提好可能係佢地手上好多貨 作為莊家總有一天係要派貨架 當然佢地可以係受害者 而家轉左其它方法收佣金<br />\n<br />\n美金的價值需要老美儲備加本土購買力再加航母戰鬥群支持 BC乜柒都唔洗就換到白花花的美金 憑乜"},{"pid":"8d0f244c2df9b8115b392db49f17374a2730a2d6","tid":485213,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:28:42.000Z","msg":"其實冇人知deepweb 個market 有幾大"},{"pid":"cd114b59f83ab6dbd6d6e0a4b63e7458aed9a46b","tid":485213,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:55:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實冇人知deepweb 個market 有幾大</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nDeepweb market唔係好大，<br />\n好多非法交易，但騙子更多<br />\n<br />\nBitcoin最大價值係用黎洗黑錢，走資，資金轉易。貪官門最愛。"},{"pid":"a08b47ea2473f137b49117c46cf065f7759a094a","tid":485213,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:58:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實冇人知deepweb 個market 有幾大</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nDeepweb market 應該唔會太大，<br />\n雖然比特幣可允許好多非法交易進行，但那裏的騙子更多。太多騙子，lack of trust。<br />\n<br />\nBitcoin 最大價值係用它黎洗黑錢，走資，資金轉移。貪官門最愛。<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1c9ed77b084f11d17327a9ee06ebd7d4cf924860","tid":485213,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T08:08:43.000Z","msg":"仲有bitcoin係連埋deepweb一齊用，先發揮到佢用黎作非法交易的價值。bitcoin不會取代deepweb。反而係deepweb和bitcoin一齊用，先有佢的價值。<br />\n<br />\n瀏覽Deepweb通常會用tor, tor係匿名瀏覽軟件。<br />\n<br />\n認識btc和deepweb的價值，先比你認識下和睇下乜叫ransomware （勒索軟件），點解可以咁公然用高強度密碼鎖你電腦再問你拿錢，警察甚至fbi都捉佢唔到 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/160745_b7b50a7abe7702a15c90fdf57be3ba80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F160745_b7b50a7abe7702a15c90fdf57be3ba80.jpg&h=14f0cdd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/160800_57ca8330b9d69e6f3cd6ffed19236f83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F160800_57ca8330b9d69e6f3cd6ffed19236f83.jpg&h=f155e491&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/160811_7a5110f7f2d0d7e7edb93f6108be47e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F160811_7a5110f7f2d0d7e7edb93f6108be47e5.jpg&h=ac210d2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e8fe7ab5d39a5c1b0bd761b1a583a4b4d27347b","tid":485213,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T08:16:37.000Z","msg":"再補加咩叫 hidden wiki<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.deepweb-sites.com/deep-web-links-2015/2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deepweb-sites.com%2Fdeep-web-links-2015%2F2%2F&d=%2FAZX5vKTfiILQ4Kc%2BEmKcJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=4b03875d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.deepweb-sites.com/deep-web-links-2015/2/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thehiddenwiki.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthehiddenwiki.org&d=%2FAZX5vKTfiILQ4Kc%2BEmKcJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=34d2100e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thehiddenwiki.org</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/The_Hidden_Wiki\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/li